Hello, Scott. I know you´re all busy with your work regarding the recent events, but I wanted to inform you that we have found something...big. See, ever since the discovery of the Infamart, we have been all too familiar with its emptiness. We were told that it was just another purposeless location of the Backrooms...or so we thought until today. 

I can´t tell you much, since all of these discoveries are new to me as well, but we know that an expedition group from the M.E.G has discovered certain  square, jelly-like bars in certain freezers from the level, all covered by blue wrapping. Testing has began in order to find any functionality or anomalous effect on these items, but to be honest those researchers in [[Level 156|156]] only want something to chew on apart from canned goods.

Since you are somewhat of a head of the [[M.E.G.|Midas´s collection team]], I just though I´d give you a heads up in all of this. Blessings.

